---

## Important Notes

| Ignored | Reason |
|---------|--------|
| `trained_models/*.pth` | Crop model is ~10MB, too large for git |
| `trained_models/*.pkl` | Soil model files |
| `datasets/` | Images are hundreds of MB |
| `__pycache__/` | Auto-generated Python cache |
| `.vscode/` | Editor specific settings |

---

## Keep These in Git

Make sure these are NOT ignored — they are essential for anyone cloning the repo:
```
app/
train_crop_model.py
train_soil_model.py
requirements.txt
CROPSAFE_AI_PROJECT_CONTEXT.md